Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:02.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suspense and deduction\Ncloses the gap between
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The love and hatred between two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:05.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori Heiji has returned
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.73,0:00:07.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He solves a mystery with Jodie
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sees through the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.54,0:00:11.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a child in appearance\Nwith the I.Q. of an adult
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.37,0:00:13.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,no case is left unsolved\Nwith Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:49.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.24,0:01:52.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the investigation records of the cases\Nthat Detective Mouri helped solve,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,were stolen from the Metropolitan Police?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.98,0:01:56.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did Detective Takagi really say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.15,0:02:01.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shh! Not so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:05.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't tell me that the thieves are
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Maybe they had a hand in this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:13.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they heard rumors that I, who was\Nsupposed to have been dead by that drug
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:16.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and if they noticed something suspicious\Nabout Kogoro Mouri's deductions,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.87,0:02:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if someone among\Nthe men in black found out that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.77,0:02:27.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi Kudo was advising Kogoro Mouri
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, my disappearance\Ncoincided with the time when
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:38.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sleeping Kogoro" started, so it wouldn't\Nsurprise me if they thought it strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:39.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet, rumors are rumors
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:44.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:47.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi Kudo isn't around anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:51.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And no one could imagine\Nthat the drug shrank me and that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:56.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm still solving cases by,\Nputting Pops to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:03:00.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if they did see me going around\Nsolving cases behind the scenes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:04.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they'd only think of me\Nas a super smart kid for my age
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, it hasn't been determined that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:09.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they're the ones who stole the records yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:10.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.45,0:03:15.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, well,... it's definite\Nthat someone is spying on Pops
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just in case,\NI have a favor to ask you!.Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:20.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:23.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You use me when you want and\Nthen you ignore me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go ask someone\Nmore reliable than me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:28.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...So,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,are you mad that I didn't tell you\Nabout the stolen records?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:33.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:36.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't be mad at me, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.85,0:03:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't help it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:42.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because she was there at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:45.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She? You mean Ail?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:46.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she knew that somebody was snooping\Nsomething around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she would refuse to go out again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:59.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I gave her my word...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:02.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And told her not to worry,\Nbecause I'd would do everything I could
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:05.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to help her if things start looking bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:07.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you see, I can't have her worrying
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:12.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, where's Haibaray
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:15.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the lab downstairs; I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:20.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, don't let her know about this
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:23.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she's not as tough as\Nshe pretends to be, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:28.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:36.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,English Teacher -v-s: Renowned\NDetective of the West" Part.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:38.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's something I don't get.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:40.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:43.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guy who stole the files\Nsent everything back
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:47.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to the Metropolitan Police,\NIn a sealed envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:51.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...\Nthe culprit probably returned the files
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because he or she already\Nfinished examining them
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.46,0:04:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:56.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they finished examining the files, then\Nwhy didn't they just throw them away?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:05:01.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would they\Ngo out of their way to send the files back
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:02.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and breed more suspicion?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:04.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The most possible explanation is that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they are trying to relay a defiant message,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:11.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're already on to all your tricks."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:15.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they're trying to lure someone out...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:19.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, in this case, the person\Nthey are trying to lure out is Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:22.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah... most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:28.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I don't get is if it's really a trap, then
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:31.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,why are they doing it in\Nsuch a complicated way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There're a lot of ways\Nto lure someone out...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:46.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What...what are you doing here, Hattori?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This old man called me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:54.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,saying that if I, your BEST FRIEND,\Ncame, I could help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I was under the impression that\NShinichi was burdened with something
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he had a hard time\Nfinding a way out{from.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.62,0:06:04.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I guess we're dealing with something\Nsimilar to grasping clouds,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so there's not much we can do
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:08.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wrong, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:12.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why{do you think Kudo came to\Ntell-'you such an important thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which he hadn't told you until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He came here either
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:20.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because he found a very important\Npiece of information, or because
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:22.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he has found a way\Nto counter attack them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:24.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:28.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, correct? Say something, will'you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:30.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You face is telling me that I hit the mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:34.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, do you remember I told you before,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:38.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that I had a brush with them\Nat Haido City Hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:39.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:41.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You went there with that\NIittle girl named Haibara
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:46.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and hunted down the\Nold man named Pisco, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been wondering for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:53.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did Pisco have\Nthe handkerchief of the party,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:55.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which he wasn't supposed to have,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:57.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when he was questioned\Nat the police station?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:02.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were seven suspects detained\Nfor questioning by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:05.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, Pisco didn't think that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his handkerchief would be\Nchecked by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:08.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.23,0:07:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone among the other six suspects,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who knew that he\Nwas gonna be checked first,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,secretly gave Pisco the handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:23.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides\NPisco, the other six suspects were
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:25.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mika Nanjo,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:26.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yasuo Mihei,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:27.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoshiharu Tahara,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:28.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naoya Tarumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:29.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naomichi Mugikura,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:31.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Chris Vineyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All six of them are celebrities-\Nwho appear frequently on the media.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:39.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is one person who\Nannounced taking a break from work,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:42.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and disappeared since that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:47.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chris Vineyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The American movie star.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chris...a second generation actress
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:07:58.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that clever and\Nbeautiful actress with big boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:07:59.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the only child of the famous actress,\NSharon Vineyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:05.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I checked on a lot of things. buts
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she's the most suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:10.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to think so though
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I want to ask a favor of you, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:18.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An internet address?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:19.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:23.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a website uploaded by fervent\Nfans of hers wanting her to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:27.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you access the site\Nand gather information?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her biographical data, interests or habits
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.27,0:08:32.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,any hot topics, anything\Nthat her fans know about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Going to the Internet Cafe any more than\NI already have, as a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:41.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,checking out foreign websites is\Ngoing to make people suspicious of me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay. I-ll try, but.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:46.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What re you gonna do\Nwith all the information?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:49.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it may come in handy one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have somebody, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:51.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
