Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:33.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's your fault she's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.07,0:19:38.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've earned your promotion\Nat the expense of her life!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even Takai seemed to be in shock\Nand at a loss for words
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:44.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that he suddenly hung up the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:48.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was told to come here,\Nand this is'what I see
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:51.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why did Mr Takai jump to his death?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's almost like I killed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't tell him, "Drop dead right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:05.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just told him the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:08.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to be held\Ncriminally responsible for killing him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:09.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true .
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:13.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can we leave now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've already answered\Nthe same questions twice!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:17.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were asked the same questions\Nbefore you came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By a foreign woman,\Na boy speaking Osaka-Ben
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:28.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and a little kid with glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:29.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:31.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me those three are...!/?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.63,0:20:34.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know where they're now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:35.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:39.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They took the key to Mr. Takai's room\Nand went to the 21st floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,21st floor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:45.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:51.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:52.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.51,0:20:55.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it'was you after all!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.35,0:21:04.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gosh» I'm really glad you held back\Nfrom entering the room!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:07.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, you can go now, leave this to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:08.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course,\Nwe-ve already checked the room thoroughly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:13.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've also taken a bunch of pictures\Nof the room!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:15.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Had the front door been locked?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:23.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah'ilt- was locked up tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.64,0:21:26.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, this room was locked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.75,0:21:29.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So. it must be suicide II'.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is what I first thought too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.99,0:21:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until I saw the curtain of\Nthe bed room window
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,from which Mr.Takai jumped!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:41.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,HUN.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:48.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's pretty much definite that\Nhe jumped from this window.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:52.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But. isn't it just that the curtain blew outward\Nbecause of the wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:54.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look closer!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The curtain was pulled down,\Nso the curtain rail is bent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.01,0:22:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And 2 or 3 hooks seem to have come off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.22,0:22:03.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is evidence that\Nhe involuntarily grabbed the curtain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.95,0:22:05.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when he came close to falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.69,0:22:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would someone trying to kill himself do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.69,0:22:12.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If so this 1s not suicide. but
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.23,0:22:14.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:19.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a homicide case...
